Popular Rap queen, Nicki Minaj has announced her retirement from music. Minaj made the announcement, Thursday, on her Twitter page. Giving reasons for her decision, Minaj said she was retiring from music to concentrate on her family. She asked her fans to keep supporting her till death. She wrote; “I’ve decided to retire and have my family. I know you guys are happy now. “To my fans, keep ‘reppin me, do it til da death of me, X in the box- cuz ain’t nobody checkin me. Love you for LIFE.” (sic) Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.